🚀 LORAFRAME (IDLock Engine)
Persistent Character Memory & AI Video Generation System

LORAFRAME is an advanced AI pipeline designed to generate consistent, evolving digital characters. It combines episodic memory, LLM reasoning, and identity-preservation techniques to create permanent digital actors that maintain visual consistency across thousands of images and videos.

✨ Key Features
🔒 Identity Retention (IDLock)
Uses InsightFace and embedding matching
Ensures face consistency across generations
🧠 Episodic Memory System
Characters remember past scenes, clothing changes, and injuries
Powered by RAG and vector databases
⚡ Smart Prompt Engine
Converts simple prompts into rich cinematic descriptions
Uses Groq (Llama 3) for context-aware generation
🎬 Multi-Modal Output
Generates high-quality images and videos
Uses Google Gemini, Imagen, and Veo
🔁 Self-Healing Loop
Detects identity drift
Automatically refines outputs to maintain consistency
