🏗️ Architecture Overview
User interacts with FastAPI Gateway
Requests are queued using Redis
Workers handle generation, refinement, memory tracking, and LoRA training
Data stored in PostgreSQL, Vector DB, and Object Storage
AI models generate images/videos and validator ensures identity consistency
